    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220970/extras/29d228755dd6097370339a66cd993902.poster.avif?t=1744738192\" width=600 height=151 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220970/extras/29d228755dd6097370339a66cd993902.webm?t=1744738192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>很简单 - Calm Cove是一个舒适的建造游戏，你所要做的就是在沉浸于大自然舒缓的声音中建造你的小梦想岛。没有压力，没有管理，没有战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220970/extras/0f8903298ecd9c365f395d1259418857.poster.avif?t=1744738192\" width=600 height=151 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220970/extras/0f8903298ecd9c365f395d1259418857.webm?t=1744738192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>创造力会得到回报 - 塑造岛屿的可能性数不胜数。你甚至可以更进一步，按照自己喜欢的方式装饰建筑物本身！<br><br>你的岛屿变得生机勃勃 - 村民们会定居下来，四处漫步，因为谁不想住在靠近海洋的美丽岛屿上呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220970/extras/e1629fa10d47cb4b7fab6106cda90cbd.poster.avif?t=1744738192\" width=600 height=151 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220970/extras/e1629fa10d47cb4b7fab6106cda90cbd.webm?t=1744738192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
